                   All rights reserved.

epicon is console terminal software.epicon is named Easy Personal
Interface  CoNsole.  However it is a lie though it is that a name
doesn't matter.  As a matter of fact, it is my wife's  nickname..
My  wife's name is Emiko so epicon is that female fox Hi.  epicon
is designed for router configuration  tool,  be  small,  portable
,simple.   epicon  is  a serial line or a TCP/IP connection which
works on the pepolinux.  epicon call protocol of Zmodem,  Xmodem,
kermit  from  the  inside.  Use gkermit together with epicon that
the patch of indicating a counter was made because it is a little
gentle.

